              <abstract>
                <title>ABSTRACT</title>
                <p>The draft genome sequences of six <italic>Bacillus</italic> strains, isolated from the International Space Station and belonging to the <italic>Bacillus anthracis</italic>-<italic>B. cereus</italic>-<italic>B. thuringiensis</italic> group, are presented here. These strains were isolated from the Japanese Experiment Module (one strain), U.S. Harmony Node 2 (three strains), and Russian Segment Zvezda Module (two strains).</p>
              </abstract>
